What is loops?
   The repetition of code is called loop.
   Each reptition is called iteration.
   In another words,
       Running same line of code for a certain number of times is called loop.
FOR LOOP:
   when you know,how many times your loop needs to iterate then you can use for loop.
WHILE LOOP:
    When you have the kind of loop where you need to sstop the loop based on certain condition ,you can use while loop.
